OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start this morning
OL,6,Fwith the odd light shower. Otherwise
OL,7,Fit will be a dry day with cloud
OL,8,Fbreaking to give some sunshine this
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry with some late sunshine
OL,12,Fthis evening. Staying dry for the rest
OL,13,Fof the night but clouding over from
OL,14,Fthe east. Most of the west coast
OL,15,Fremaining clear.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FA dry day with overnight
OL,18,Fcloud gradually breaking up to leave
OL,19,Fsome afternoon sunshine. Best of the
OL,20,Fsunshine across the west where it will
OL,21,Ffeel warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
