OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Fand settled with plenty of sunshine,
OL,7,Fovernight low cloud in the east soon
OL,8,Fburning off. Feeling warm in the
OL,9,Fsunshine.
